    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_09_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_09_01-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃーん！　こっちこっち！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.2333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 2966.6666667,
          "startTime": 7.2
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 7.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_09_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_09_01-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "渚！　遅くなってごめんなさい\n撮影の仕事が長引いちゃって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 12.9333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_09_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_09_01-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様～！　琴乃ちゃんが来てくれて良かったよ\n隣の席の圧が凄くて、一人だと心細かったんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.4481061603,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 24
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_09_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_09_01-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "圧が凄いって、隣の席に誰が……\nあ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 29.1666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "lim",
      "speakerName": "小南来夢",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-lim.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_09_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_09_01-lim001.m4a",
      "text": "ああ？　なんだ、文句あんのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 33.479999876
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_09_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_09_01-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "来夢さんにれもんさん！\nご無沙汰しています。お二人も見に来ていたんですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.5133332093,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 39.479999876
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "lim",
      "speakerName": "小南来夢",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-lim.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_09_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_09_01-lim002.m4a",
      "text": "まぁな。VENUSグランプリの\n準々決勝ともなれば、敵情視察ぐらいはするさ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.4880462624,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 46.9522221406
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "lmn",
      "speakerName": "大須賀れもん",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-lmn.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_09_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_09_01-lmn001.m4a",
      "text": "先週の月ストのライブバトルも見に行ったわよぉ\n準々決勝第一試合、悪くないパフォーマンスだったわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 56.1783201377
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "lim",
      "speakerName": "小南来夢",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-lim.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_09_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_09_01-lim003.m4a",
      "text": "あれからさらに成長したみたいじゃねーか\n一応、ベスト4進出よくやったと褒めてやるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.8333315532,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_happy-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 64.5485469341
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 64.5485469341
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_09_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_09_01-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます。でも、それはお二人もですよね\nどりきゅんもベスト4進出おめでとうございます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.6485469341,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 73.0818802674
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "lim",
      "speakerName": "小南来夢",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-lim.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_09_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_09_01-lim004.m4a",
      "text": "別にめでたかねえよ\n今のあたしらなら、あの程度の相手、勝って当たり前だ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.7333315532,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 80.7952133338
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_09_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_09_01-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "準々決勝第一試合、勝者は月のテンペスト……\n第二試合、勝者はどりきゅん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.0618800004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_09_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_09_01-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "そして今日行われる第三試合と、来週の第四試合で\nVENUSグランプリのベスト4が出揃いますね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.8618800004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 98.2285466671
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "lmn",
      "speakerName": "大須賀れもん",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-lmn.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_09_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_09_01-lmn002.m4a",
      "text": "第三試合はスリクス対トリエル\n第四試合はサニピ対リズノワ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.6333315532,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "lmn",
      "speakerName": "大須賀れもん",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-lmn.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_09_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_09_01-lmn003.m4a",
      "text": "どちらも星見プロ所属のアイドル対決だなんて\n前代未聞よねぇ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 110.6101307074
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_09_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_09_01-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "ですが、少しも意外じゃありません。どのグループも\n優勝しておかしくない実力を持っていますから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.4734441563,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 117.4101307074
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "lim",
      "speakerName": "小南来夢",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-lim.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_09_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_09_01-lim005.m4a",
      "text": "ちなみに、琴乃はどのグループが勝ち上がると\n予想してるんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.9666618347,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 122.7097450733
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_09_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_09_01-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "実力は甲乙つけがたいですから\nどこが勝ってもおかしくないと思います",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.3954071477,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 128.0097450733
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "lim",
      "speakerName": "小南来夢",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-lim.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_09_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_09_01-lim006.m4a",
      "text": "優等生過ぎてつまんねぇ回答だな\nそっちのお嬢ちゃんはどう思うんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.3333285014,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 135.3338588555
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_09_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_09_01-ngs005.m4a",
      "text": "お嬢ちゃんはやめて下さい、私の名前は伊吹渚です\nさっきも挨拶したのに、わざと言ってますよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.1005255222,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 145.9671921889
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_09_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_09_01-ngs006.m4a",
      "text": "でも……どこが勝つかは分かりませんが\n個人的に応援しているグループならあります",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 150.1671921889,
      "sfxList": []
    },
